# Supabase — the dashboard is gated behind Supabase Auth; reads run as the
# signed-in `authenticated` user (anon has no access). This is the publishable
# key (safe to ship in the browser). Copy to .env and fill in. NEVER commit .env.
# VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR-PROJECT-ref.supabase.co
 # VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=sb_publishable_xxx

# Board Pack (T-7) AI endpoint — the n8n webhook that calls Claude and returns the
# board narrative + recommendations. The Anthropic API key lives in n8n (never in
# the browser); the app POSTs the computed figure set here and validates every
# returned number against the warehouse. Import workflows/board_pack_generate.json,
# select your Anthropic credential, activate it, then paste the PRODUCTION webhook
# URL here. Leave unset to disable generation (the figures + gaps still render).
# VITE_BOARDPACK_WEBHOOK_URL=https://YOUR-n8n-host/webhook/board-pack-generate

# Board-pack PPTX (Gamma) endpoint — the n8n webhook that sends the app-built
# Markdown brief to Gamma's Generate API (textMode:"preserve", exportAs:"pptx") and
# returns the deck as base64. The Gamma API key lives in n8n ($env.GAMMA_API_KEY).
# Import workflows/gamma-generation.json, set the credential, activate, then paste
# the PRODUCTION webhook URL here. Powers the Board Pack "PPTX" action. Leave unset
# to disable it (Branded PDF + quick PDF still work).
# NOTE: replaces the retired Google-Slides "Branded deck" (VITE_SLIDESDECK_WEBHOOK_URL).
# VITE_GAMMA_WEBHOOK_URL=https://YOUR-n8n-host/webhook/board-pack-gamma

# Branded Board Pack PDF (Route 3) endpoint — the n8n webhook that renders the
# CWSI-branded board-pack HTML to PDF via Gotenberg (headless Chromium), returned
# as base64. Matches the artifact design AND keeps selectable text. Import
# workflows/board_pack_pdf_render.json, set the Gotenberg URL in the "Gotenberg:
# render" node, activate, then paste the PRODUCTION webhook URL here. Needs a
# reachable Gotenberg instance (docker run --rm -p 3000:3000 gotenberg/gotenberg:8).
# Leave unset to hide/disable the Branded PDF action (quick PDF/PPTX still work).
# VITE_BOARDPACK_PDF_WEBHOOK_URL=https://YOUR-n8n-host/webhook/board-pack-pdf
